      <paragraph>
        <num>•</num>
        <content>
          <p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/200092/FINAL_Facing_the_Future__3_md.pdf"><u>Sir Ken Knight, Facing the Future: Findings from the review of efficiencies and operations in fire and rescue authorities in England, 17 May 2013</u></a></p>
        </content>
      </paragraph>
      <paragraph>
